PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FThe King and Queen will meet with US
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump in person five
OL,8,Ftimes over four days as they try to
OL,9,Fpatch up the strained relations
OL,10,Fbetween the US and UK amid the
OL,11,Fconflict in Iran.
OL,13,FBritish diplomats and palace officials
OL,14,Fadmit these are challenging times, but
OL,15,Fthey are confident King Charles has
OL,16,Fthe experience to make it a success
OL,17,Fand enjoys the respect of President
OL,18,FTrump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FHowever, everyone involved in the
OL,7,Fvisit admits it is the most risky
OL,8,Fdiplomatic trip of King Charles' reign
OL,9,Fso far.
OL,11,FThe official state visit to the United
OL,12,FStates is taking place at the end of
OL,13,FApril in Washington DC, New York and
OL,14,FVirginia, and despite the barbed
OL,15,Fcomments Trump has made about the UK
OL,16,Fin recent weeks, Downing Street is
OL,17,Fdetermined it should still go ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FBut King Charles and Queen Camilla are
OL,7,Funable to meet any survivors of
OL,8,FJeffrey Epstein's abuse because of the
OL,9,Frisk that any such meeting could
OL,10,Fprejudice the ongoing police
OL,11,Finvestigations into Epstein in the UK.
OL,13,FIt is not the King and Queen's
OL,14,Fdecision to visit the United States at
OL,15,Fthis time; they have been asked to go
OL,16,Fby the UK government and have agreed
OL,17,Fto do so.
OL,19,FThe official purpose of the trip is to
OL,20,Fmark the 250th anniversary of the US
OL,21,FDeclaration of Independence in 1776.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FAnd, as Buckingham Palace appeared to
OL,7,Facknowledge, the historic relationship
OL,8,Fbetween the two countries is more than
OL,9,Fabout any individual occupant of the
OL,10,FOval Office.
OL,12,FThe last "King of America" was George
OL,13,FIII, who was on the throne during and
OL,14,Fafter the American War of Independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FA Palace spokesperson said: "This is
OL,7,Fcelebrating a partnership between two
OL,8,Fnations and two peoples. It is a
OL,9,Frelationship that has survived many
OL,10,Fpresidencies and, of course, many
OL,11,Freigns, and will no doubt continue to
OL,12,Fdo so long into the future."
OL,14,FDonald Trump has already been afforded
OL,15,Ftwo state visits to the UK, but this
OL,16,Fis the first time a British monarch
OL,17,Fhas visited the US since Queen
OL,18,FElizabeth in 2007.
OL,26,@nD@]OUtD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FKing Charles has also accepted an
OL,7,Finvitation to address a joint session
OL,8,Fof the United States Congress,
OL,9,Fsomething his mother last did in 1991
OL,10,F- shortly after the first Gulf War.
OL,12,FBut that speech came at a time when
OL,13,Fthe US and UK were on the same page
OL,14,Fconcerning the conflict in the Middle
OL,15,FEast, unlike now when the US president
OL,16,Fhas given Sir Keir Starmer several
OL,17,Ftongue lashings over his refusal to
OL,18,Fget involved in the US-Israeli attacks
OL,19,Fon Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FTrump has said Starmer is "no Winston
OL,7,FChurchill", he picked on his voice,
OL,8,Fshared social media posts mocking his
OL,9,FBritish counterpart and called Royal
OL,10,FNavy warships "toys" compared to
OL,11,FAmerican ones.
OL,13,FIn the House of Commons on Monday,
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,15,Fsaid the visit should be called off.
OL,17,FSir Ed told MPs: "I really fear for
OL,18,Fwhat Trump might say or do while our
OL,19,FKing is forced to stand by his side.
OL,20,FWe cannot put His Majesty in that
OL,21,Fposition."
OL,26,@}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FBut the prime minister put his faith
OL,7,Fin the so-called 'soft-power' of the
OL,8,Fmonarchy, which he said, "is often
OL,9,Fable to reach through the decades on a
OL,10,Fsituation like this".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe King and Queen will be welcomed to
OL,18,FWashington DC on 27 April, with a
OL,19,Fprivate tea at the White House hosted
OL,20,Fby the President and First Lady.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FThere will also be a formal ceremonial
OL,7,Fmilitary review the following day in
OL,8,Fthe White House grounds, plus a
OL,9,Fbilateral meeting between King Charles
OL,10,Fand President Trump.
OL,12,FOnly stills photographers have been
OL,13,Finvited into the Oval Office, which
OL,14,Flimits the chance of Donald Trump
OL,15,Fsaying something awkward in front of
OL,16,FTV cameras.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FFollowing the speech to senators and
OL,7,Frepresentatives in Congress, the King
OL,8,Fand Queen will attend a state dinner
OL,9,Fat the White House with speeches from
OL,10,Fboth principals.
OL,12,FWe can assume that the words will be
OL,13,Fsigned off by both American and
OL,14,FBritish diplomats, but no one can ever
OL,15,Fbe confident that Trump will stick to
OL,16,Fhis script and avoid making any off-
OL,17,Fthe-cuff remarks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FIn New York on 29 April, the King and
OL,7,FQueen will honour those who were
OL,8,Fkilled on 9/11 and meet serving
OL,9,Femergency service personnel, in what
OL,10,Fis the 25th anniversary year of the
OL,11,F2001 terrorist attacks.
OL,13,FThere will also be several other
OL,14,Fevents in Manhattan, but it has not
OL,15,Fbeen confirmed if the royals will meet
OL,16,Fthe newly elected mayor, Zohran
OL,17,FMamdani.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FOn their final day in the US, they
OL,7,Fwill travel to a town in Virginia and
OL,8,Fa national park to meet Americans who
OL,9,Fare starting the 250th anniversary
OL,10,Fcelebrations ahead of this year's July
OL,11,F4th Independence Day.
OL,13,FWhat the King and Queen will not be
OL,14,Fable to do on the trip is see those
OL,15,FEpstein survivors who have written to
OL,16,Fthe palace asking for a meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FThere is currently a criminal
OL,7,Finvestigation in the UK into the
OL,8,FKing's younger brother, Andrew
OL,9,FMountbatten-Windsor, for the offence
OL,10,Fof misconduct in public office.
OL,12,FAndrew has consistently denied any
OL,13,Fwrongdoing, but he was stripped of his
OL,14,Fprince title, his dukedom and his home
OL,15,Fin Windsor.
OL,17,FOther police assessments are going on
OL,18,Finto claims of trafficking young women
OL,19,Finto the UK for sex.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FThe former Prince Andrew has
OL,7,Fconsistently denied any wrongdoing,
OL,8,Fbut he was stripped of his prince
OL,9,Ftitle, his dukedom and his home in
OL,10,FWindsor over what the palace called
OL,11,Fhis "errors of judgement".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FA Buckingham Palace source said: "We
OL,7,Ffully understand and appreciate the
OL,8,Fsurvivors' position, but can only
OL,9,Freiterate that our position is clear
OL,10,Fthat anything that could potentially
OL,11,Fimpact on ongoing police inquiries and
OL,12,Fassessments and any potential criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation that could result from
OL,14,Fthat would be to the detriment of the
OL,15,Fsurvivors themselves in their pursuit
OL,16,Fof justice."
OL,18,FHowever small the risk, it is one
OL,19,Fpalace officials are not prepared to
OL,20,Ftake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FThe royal source pointed to the
OL,7,F"robust comments" and "actions" the
OL,8,FKing and Queen have previously taken
OL,9,Fon this issue and pointed to Queen
OL,10,FCamilla's "long-term advocacy in
OL,11,Fsupport of the victims and survivors
OL,12,Fof all forms of domestic and sexual
OL,13,Fabuse".
OL,15,FIt's understood that the Queen will
OL,16,Fmeet with organisations advocating for
OL,17,Fsurvivors and victims at other
OL,18,Fengagements during her time in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776269466
OL,3,CKing to charm Trump in US state visit
OL,4,Cto smooth UK-US relations
OL,6,FOverall, it will be a challenging few
OL,7,Fdays in the United States and British
OL,8,Fdiplomats will be holding their
OL,9,Fcollective breaths that Trump will be
OL,10,Fon his best behaviour.
OL,12,FThat, however, is something about
OL,13,Fwhich no one can be certain.
OL,15,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,16,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,17,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,18,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
